    "description": "《三国演义之蜀汉传奇》是作者闲暇之余对于游戏制作的初步探索，该作品在一定程度上借鉴了八十年代FC上的《三国演义之吞食天地》系列，并对发生在中华大地上壮阔灿烂的三国历史剧情加以改编而诞生的历史题材回合制RGP游戏。作者怀揣游戏开发的梦想，初出茅庐踏足游戏行业，还请大家多多指教。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/3c32bab7f87e007e8eca72eff25ab175.poster.avif?t=1750627926\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/3c32bab7f87e007e8eca72eff25ab175.webm?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/3c32bab7f87e007e8eca72eff25ab175.mp4?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【丰富的武将角色】</h2>刘备、关羽、张飞、赵云、诸葛亮、曹操……耳熟能详的角色多达200人，此外游戏中着重描写一位名为钟离慕雪的架空人物，影射作者幻想自己身处三国乱世的学识、能力、胆识、处世和形象。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/7cd9f0ebb1cac0513cd1677c064c62cc.avif?t=1750627926\" width=576 height=288 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/321fb92fb2f61546a395c35fedfcba96.avif?t=1750627926\" width=576 height=288 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【100多种武将技能以及谋略】</h2>每一种技能或谋略都有独立的演出动画，为战斗增添乐趣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/cf8e6929ca3c6fef491c2cc27d1fcbe0.poster.avif?t=1750627926\" width=576 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/cf8e6929ca3c6fef491c2cc27d1fcbe0.webm?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/cf8e6929ca3c6fef491c2cc27d1fcbe0.mp4?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/5e6c4e52c34c08111d3e00a8cc550cb8.poster.avif?t=1750627926\" width=576 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/5e6c4e52c34c08111d3e00a8cc550cb8.webm?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/5e6c4e52c34c08111d3e00a8cc550cb8.mp4?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/b5f0667d3469d640c9eddc62f544261d.poster.avif?t=1750627926\" width=576 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/b5f0667d3469d640c9eddc62f544261d.webm?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/b5f0667d3469d640c9eddc62f544261d.mp4?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/07ddeed0213b7b33ae272504dea7d126.poster.avif?t=1750627926\" width=576 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/07ddeed0213b7b33ae272504dea7d126.webm?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/07ddeed0213b7b33ae272504dea7d126.mp4?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【丰富的武器装备以及饰品】</h2>游戏中可装备的物品种类有剑、枪、斧、弓、爪、刀、扇、身体护甲、头部护甲、手部护甲、脚部护甲、盾牌护甲、书籍、项链、戒指，并且每一种装备都会生成孔洞，用以镶嵌宝石。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【极具策略的回合制战斗】</h2>战斗系统采用回合制战斗系统，你拥有足够的时间进行思考，准好好挑战各式各样的关卡了吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/f2fabfba1c52d403e20b75ef1d4bc6cb.poster.avif?t=1750627926\" width=576 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/f2fabfba1c52d403e20b75ef1d4bc6cb.webm?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1557690/extras/f2fabfba1c52d403e20b75ef1d4bc6cb.mp4?t=1750627926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【丰富的三国历史剧情】</h2>游戏的剧情叙事以刘备军为主要视角，时间线从刘备讨伐袁术开始到击败魏国一统中国结束，还原了绝大部分与刘备军相关的三国演义小说剧情。",
